[Nouns] pendency, dependency; suspension, hanging; pedicel, pedicle, peduncle; tail, train, flap, skirt, pigtail, pendulum; hangnail.
peg, knob, button, hook, nail, stud, ring, staple, tenterhook; fastening [more]; spar, horse.
[Verbs] be pendent; hang, depend, swing, dangle; swag; daggle, flap, trail, flow; beetle.
suspend, hang, sling, hook up, hitch, fasten to, append.
[Adjectives] pendent, pendulous; pensile; hanging; beetling, jutting over, overhanging, projecting; dependent; suspended; loose, flowing.
having a peduncle; pedunculate, tailed, caudate.
